  <h4 class="title">Technologies</h4>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <h5>General Purpose</h5>
        <p>
          Java, Python, C, Scala.
        </p>

        <h5>Web &amp; Mobile</h5>
        <p>
          React, React Native, Redux, Flask, HTML, CSS.
        </p>

